snippet.title: Astral Guardians : Cyber Fantasy Gameplay (Android/iOS)
snippet.description:
[Astral Guardians] is a 3D action RPG that puts you on a mission to save an entire kingdom.
Here, you will complete missions and challenges that are the strangest warriors in the kingdom. During this adventurous journey, you will meet various animal races. Make contracts with passion, acquire powerful weapons, match different skills to increase your strength, refine with the strong dark forces and become the strongest in the continent. Save the devastated country and write the story of your adventure.

Raise your weapons and love!

Link Download 
Play Store : https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.eyougame.idxj
App Store : https://apps.apple.com/us/app/id1524581682

Size : 1.10 GB
Control  : Auto
Internet : Online
Language : English
Device : Android
